ng the food takes to get to that part.  The staff did an okay job but I think their day jobs force them to do their best to make sure that they get the job done faster.  So you could say their day jobs force them to do their best, but I am a bit biased on that.\n\nThe prices here are okay, but I think you can get better stuff if you want at the same quality of stuff at the chain supermarkets as Dollar Tree and all that.  I think that Dollar Tree prices for the quality of food is better and they make better quality food than this one.  Like I said before, I did not think much of it before.\n\nOverall, if you come and go when the mood strikes you will not be disappointed!<|endoftext|>
